{"word":"ἐλαφρός","slug":"ἐλαφρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐλαφρός, ά, όν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>ἐλαχύς</el> ‘small’] <b>light,</b> in sense of being easy to bear or endure <b><a href='B:470 11:30'>Mt 11:30</a>.</b> As noun <el>τὸ ἐλαφρόν</el> lightness <b><a href='B:540 4:17'>2 Cor 4:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐλαφρία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔλαχε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}